  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  65 years of age or older

          -  type 2 diabetes managed with diet or oral hypoglycemic agents

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  using insulin to manage diabetes

          -  baseline of pre-session blood glucose reading equal to or greater than 10 mmol/L

          -  any medical condition that would limit the ability to perform activity portion of the
             study

          -  people not comfortable exercising on a stationary bicycle

          -  subject answers yes to one of more of the questions in the Physical Activity
             Readiness Questionnaire
      </textblock>
